{"word":"H6315 - פּוּחַ - pûwach - poo'akh - Blow","slug":"H6315","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פּוּחַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pûwach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>poo'akh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Blow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05D7; - pu&#x0302;ach</b> - <i>poo'-akh</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>puff</i>, that is, blow with the breath or air; hence to <i>fan</i> (as a breeze), to <i>utter</i>, to <i>kindle</i> (a fire), to <i>scoff: - </i>blow (upon), break, puff, bring into a snare, speak, utter."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6316\">H6316</a>, <a href=\"#/H6317\">H6317</a>, <a href=\"#/H6318\">H6318</a>, <a href=\"#/H6319\">H6319</a>, <a href=\"#/H6320\">H6320</a>, <a href=\"#/H6321\">H6321</a>, <a href=\"#/H6322\">H6322</a>, <a href=\"#/H6368\">H6368</a>"}]}